The paper discusses the use of robot technology and autonomous agents in order-fulfillment centers, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), systems and control (cs.SY), and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus on path finding and optimization also suggests a potential fit with the cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) category. However, given the emphasis on AI and robotics, cs.AI and cs.RO are the most likely categories.
